data.value: A right-handed batsman and a medium pacer by trade, Marcus Stoinis, is an Australian all-rounder. Stoinis was a member of the Australian side that featured in the 2008 Under-19 World Cup in Malaysia, a team that included players like Steven Smith, Phil Hughes, James Pattinson, Josh Hazlewood and James Faulkner.
